Jack Betts writes on politics and life in The Carolinas for the Charlotte Observer's Editorial page.
Blog: This Old State <http://jackbetts.blogspot.com/><http://jackbetts.blogspot.com/>
E-mail Jack <mailto:jbetts@charlotteobserver.com><mailto:jbetts@charlotteobserver.com>
